Class Graph

java.lang.Object
Graph
public class Graph extends Object
This class is a template for the graph data structure. It uses the Node object to create nodes in the graph and then makes the adjacency list. nodes : ArrayList of Nodes in the graph. nodeCount : an integer to store total number of nodes in the graph.
Author:
Shadab Khan
